msgid "5 Minute"
msgstr "5 Nóiméad"

msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "Cealaigh"

msgid "Clear data for all interfaces"
msgstr "Sonraí soiléire do gach comhéadain"

msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Cumraíocht"

msgid "Could not load graph, no data available:"
msgstr "Níorbh fhéidir graf a luchtú, níl aon sonraí ar fáil:"

msgid "Daily"
msgstr "laethúil"

msgid "Delete"
msgstr "Scrios"

msgid "Delete data for ALL interfaces"
msgstr "Scrios sonraí do GACH comhéadain"

msgid "Delete interface <em>%h</em>"
msgstr "Scrios an comhéadan <em>%h</em>"

msgid "Delete…"
msgstr "Scrios…"

msgid "Grant access to LuCI app vnstat2"
msgstr "Deonaigh rochtain ar app LuCI vnstat2"

msgid "Graphs"
msgstr "Graif"

msgid "Hourly"
msgstr "in aghaidh na huaire"

msgid "Interface"
msgstr "Comhéadan"

msgid "Interfaces"
msgstr "Comhéadain"

msgid "Loading graphs…"
msgstr "Grafa á lódáil…"

msgid "Monitor interfaces"
msgstr "Monatóireacht a dhéanamh ar chomhéadain"

msgid "Monthly"
msgstr "go míosúil"

msgid ""
"No monitored interfaces have been found. Go to the configuration to enable "
"monitoring for one or more interfaces."
msgstr ""
"Ní bhfuarthas aon chomhéadain mhonatóireachta. Téigh go dtí an chumraíocht "
"chun monatóireacht a dhéanamh ar chomhéadain amháin nó níos mó."

msgid "No unconfigured interfaces found in database."
msgstr "Níor aimsíodh aon chomhéadain neamhchumraithe sa bhunachar sonraí."

msgid "Summary"
msgstr "Achoimre"

msgid ""
"The data will be removed from the database permanently. This cannot be "
"undone."
msgstr ""
"Bainfear na sonraí den bhunachar sonraí go buan. Ní féidir é seo a chealú."

msgid ""
"The interface will be removed from the database permanently. This cannot be "
"undone."
msgstr ""
"Bainfear an comhéadan den bhunachar sonraí go buan. Ní féidir é seo a chealú."

msgid ""
"The selected interfaces are automatically added to the vnStat database upon "
"startup."
msgstr ""
"Cuirtear na comhéadain roghnaithe go huathoibríoch leis an mbunachar sonraí "
"vnStat nuair a thosaítear."

msgid ""
"These interfaces are present in the vnStat database, but are not configured "
"above."
msgstr ""
"Tá na comhéadain seo i mbunachar sonraí vnStat, ach níl siad cumraithe thuas."

msgid "Top"
msgstr "Barr"

msgid "Traffic Monitor"
msgstr "Monatóir Tráchta"

msgid "Unconfigured interfaces"
msgstr "Comhéadain neamhchumraithe"

msgid "Warning: The service is not running, graphs will not be updated!"
msgstr "Rabhadh: Níl an tseirbhís ag rith, ní dhéanfar graif a nuashonrú!"

msgid "Yearly"
msgstr "Bliantúil"

msgid "vnStat"
msgstr "vnStat"

msgid "vnStat Graphs"
msgstr "Grafaicí vnStat"

msgid ""
"vnStat is a network traffic monitor for Linux that keeps a log of network "
"traffic for the selected interface(s)."
msgstr ""
"Is monatóir tráchta líonra é vnStat le haghaidh Linux a choinníonn loga de "
"thrácht líonra don chomhéadan/na comhéadain roghnaithe."
